<div type="definition">
<p>PEACEFUL:at-ease BECAUSE what one NEEDS is PREPARED:provided.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for material and psychological comfort is ān 安.</p>
